welcome_message_body: "Welcome to Rochedale, Australia! Get ready to experience the charm of our vibrant city known for its breathtaking natural beauty. We invite you to fully immerse yourself in our culture and explore all that Rochedale has to offer. Enjoy your stay!"

terminals.name: International Terminal
terminals.description: Handles all international flights and has a variety of amenities such as duty-free shops and restaurants.

terminals.name: Domestic Terminal
terminals.description: Serves all domestic flights and offers a range of services including lounges and retail stores.

wifi.note: Free Wi-Fi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Dunwich Airport is a modern and efficient facility that serves both domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: Cargo Terminal
terminals.description: The cargo terminal at Dunwich Airport is equipped to handle a variety of goods and is an important hub for the transportation of goods in and out of Australia.

wifi.note: Passengers can enjoy complimentary WiFi throughout the airport. Simply connect to the network and follow the prompts to access the internet.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.
